- Repository interfaces provided by Spring Data JPA, such as CrudRepository

- CrudRepository actually impilicitly a bean

- Dependency is like you declare another class and inject it as parameter in th constructor

- Use Iterable<Class name> 

- To test the method with defined mapping "curl localhost:4001/plants"

- To test POST Method 
curl -X POST <URL/base> -H <Content-type> -d <parameter>
